title: КликКлак шоу
overview: "ClickClack Show" is the TV version of the popular YouTube project. Not only the regular participants (Eldar Jarakhov, Yuri Muzychenko, Ilya Satir, Andrei Stariy, Danya Kraster and Andrei Prokofyev), but also the guest stars will be tested.Project host and showrunner Ruslan Usachev prepared a lot of crazy contests: the race on the walker, the run on the sticky floor, the battle in the Coliseum, giant cakes, ice pool with a surprise, jumping through breaking glass, the shower of insects, the electric shock test and much more.
